section.p:
You can explore your data in several different ways, using
[filters]({{ site.baseurl }}#explore-filters), [breakdowns]({{
site.baseurl }}#explore-breakdowns), [metrics]({{ site.baseurl
}}#explore-metrics), or [comparisons]({{ site.baseurl
}}#explore-comparisons).

After you make a change to your Answer, you may want to go back to
an earlier version of your Answer. You can click the Back icon
![]({{ site.baseurl }}/images/icon-arrow-left-20px.png){: .inline}
to go back one step, or the Reset icon ![]({{ site.baseurl
}}/images/icon-reset-20px.png){: .inline} to go back to the
original answer.
